00:17:35,080 --> 00:17:38,240
so what I'd do is go and buy
a smaller dishwasher,

295
00:17:38,320 --> 00:17:40,480
or I'd borrow a slightly bigger car,

296
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,560
