345
00:20:38,520 --> 00:20:41,320
and scrap it,
and so on and so forth.

346
00:20:41,720 --> 00:20:45,080
If you're not worried about
the second-hand value of your car,

347
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,640
it's so liberating.

